{"tid":208911,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"因為你 我迷失了","createTime":"2017-04-19T22:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T13:38:50.000Z","uid":50839,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f67da1ab5f6268e3fac4274189ada5470ba4b19a","tid":208911,"uid":50839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T22:31:43.000Z","msg":"其實會唔會係諗太多 <br />\n根本大家諗多咗<br />\n其實過去又有咩問題<br />\n肯改過都係一種磨練<br />\n我就算估中你諗咩<br />\n我都唔敢講<br />\n因為我好想聽你講<br />\n<br />\n之前嘅一切<br />\n係咪真心<br />\n如今大家突然變咗陌路人咁<br />\n我冇辦法接受<br />\n<br />\n你話過你投入咗<br />\n我都好投入<br />\n既然一切就緒<br />\n點解又要咁嘅態度對我呢？<br />\n你話自己嘅不是<br />\n我何嘗冇呢<br />\n<br />\n我出自真心<br />\n咁同你傾<br />\n由開始到宜家<br />\n我實在抽唔到身<br />\n我唔恨你<br />\n因為你做嘅一切都似係內疚<br />\n如果你唔想再做一個傷害我嘅人<br />\n又徘徊喺痛嘅邊緣<br />\n我寧願你肯坦誠講哂出嚟<br />\n<br />\n我知道自己又試 自以為是<br />\n但我好想你知<br />\n我係好真心咁鍾意你<br />\n我冇呃過你<br />\n<br />\n你可以令我放低過去<br />\n難道你唔可以咩？<br />\n<br />\n犯過嘅錯可以彌補<br />\n但錯過嘅感情就追唔翻<br />\n你當初同我講嘅<br />\n今日你忘記咗嗎？<br />\n<br />\n唔想錯過.............<br />\n呢句說話你係咪真心講？"},{"pid":"b2b8066a8a4ecc9ad767429fa7c2a78c77d73615","tid":208911,"uid":54278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T22:32:02.000Z","msg":"關我撚事"},{"pid":"224dd739f7a64494758ccd3776f93d2a5d1e7373","tid":208911,"uid":34680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T22:33:45.000Z","msg":"冇人會想一而再再而三錯過"},{"pid":"adc335ac969f27496174206a985d602faa4c624b","tid":208911,"uid":50839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T22:35:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇人會想一而再再而三錯過</blockquote><br />\n我同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab055e67c5ac5986c18ce44d1452181b936624a0","tid":208911,"uid":50839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T22:40:28.000Z","msg":"我唔知你仲鍾唔鍾意我<br />\n但你又知我痛苦<br />\n仲叫我去尋夢<br />\n但係我嘅夢想根本唔係咁<br />\n我嘅夢想係你<br />\n我認煩膠<br />\n唔敢打擾你<br />\n掙扎好耐"},{"pid":"7df896caa4b6e2234fdbdede485abbe9d1c61175","tid":208911,"uid":50839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T22:49:10.000Z","msg":"你話呢世都難搵個好似我咁嘅人<br />\n所以唔想錯過<br />\n你宜家揀咁嘅做法<br />\n唔通係諗住為我好<br />\n定係純粹你自私？"},{"pid":"30624a61b64099f82f9897b686e564276a7704fe","tid":208911,"uid":50839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T22:58:44.000Z","msg":"呢種欲哭無淚嘅心情<br />\n真係好難受"},{"pid":"ecb3b38d8c624f0a5218141a04ecdfdddf266b22","tid":208911,"uid":106067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T23:02:41.000Z","msg":"轉做sp咪幾好"},{"pid":"5cb75db22644283ce713eed34f51f4af187e4c15","tid":208911,"uid":50839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T23:05:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>轉做sp咪幾好</blockquote><br />\n我地唔係咁嘅人"},{"pid":"327d7b7ce2f571f625e4177dac8df81c55c4ee69","tid":208911,"uid":68783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T00:05:11.000Z","msg":"過去發生左d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a54a5914bf177e22b3e12b19674be464d0a86d","tid":208911,"uid":101550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02:38:47.000Z","msg":"你地讀緊書定做緊野？"},{"pid":"2690db5bd0a9dd5cb5937cf5698788a7cf09b981","tid":208911,"uid":26001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02:42:41.000Z","msg":"就算分開 不要去憎恨"},{"pid":"3e592db46727a52d4cd111549675149e02e1696f","tid":208911,"uid":101550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:25:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地讀緊書定做緊野？</blockquote><br />\n你好似一個我識得嘅人"},{"pid":"9a319f43b77ba755d670ce35578f30ec23e34e53","tid":208911,"uid":50839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T11:33:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你地讀緊書定做緊野？</blockquote><br />\n你好似一個我識得嘅人</blockquote><br />\n可能啦<br />\n可以加我tg<br />\nMochiaaaa"},{"pid":"9e772e14744a6a9f8c92716b4000e35faff79c26","tid":208911,"uid":54439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T11:36:13.000Z","msg":"我錯過 但搵唔翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08859b835a4b37ecd95eace497ae06965efeeaf8","tid":208911,"uid":50839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T11:49:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我錯過 但搵唔翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔知搵唔搵得翻<br />\n我好似麻木咗<br />\n可能再都唔會愛第二個"},{"pid":"f85f4d1cfab28feea930033cad68ddcad66ef7a7","tid":208911,"uid":33041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:35:02.000Z","msg":"但我令唔到人放低過去<br />\n我盡左力<br />\n但我做嘅野只係感動到我自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59945698293019a70e3f53cabfe21c8497648f88","tid":208911,"uid":50839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T13:38:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但我令唔到人放低過去<br />\n我盡左力<br />\n但我做嘅野只係感動到我自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係你做得唔夠仆街"}]}